{"tid":638212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共發封海令　傳為新航母試航清場","createTime":"2018-04-22T13:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T02:57:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8c95ff80219bc9003e3e76dc71a0a49face3ede4","tid":638212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180422/20369092?_ga=2.48416422.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369092%3F_ga%3D2.48416422.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=rwHfFTi%2BbPbufjMtzjzA%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2d1a3727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369092%3F_ga%3D2.48416422.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=d6617d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180422/20369092?_ga=2.48416422.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共發封海令　傳為新航母試航清場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/a1005b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2Fa1005b.gif&h=8c6062ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■首艘國產航母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新航母要試航？解放軍演習頻頻，遼寧海事局前日又連發三個禁航通告。由當日起至28日，在渤海北部執行軍事任務。內地軍事迷盛傳國產首艘航母或在4月23日海軍節試航，但內地軍事評論員則否定，認為只是遼寧艦將繼續實戰演習的可能性較大。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出動遼寧號機會較大<br />\n<br />\n解放軍繼本月12日上午在南海海域舉行海上閱兵，18日在泉州對出海域進行實彈演後，遼寧海事局網站在上周五（20日）連發三條航行警告，一是由4月20日至27日在渤海海峽與黃海北部海域將執行軍事任務，任何船隻在上述時間內不得進入通告中指定的大連對開海域；二是由4月23日至26日，在秦皇島對開渤海海域有軍事行動；三是由4月23日至28日在葫蘆島對開渤海北部有軍事任務。<br />\n<br />\n內地軍事迷期待中國首艘國產航母或在期間試航，有分析指，警航範圍附近的遼寧大連正是中國首艘國產航母的建造地，而葫蘆島興城附近又有殲15航母艦載機訓練基地，加上4月23日是中共「海軍節」，國產航母很可能「驚喜呈現」。不過，觀察者網軍事評論員則指，根據遼寧海事局發表的禁航通告，將進行「實彈射擊」，而國產首艘航母的海試預計還沒有到這個階段。另一方面，遼寧號前日通過台灣海峽後，繼續向北航行，應該是前往這一海區進行海上實戰演習的可能性較大。<br />\n<br />\n新浪網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n急流中練習　桂林龍舟翻側17死<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n細路冇心之失　大肚婆kick跌報復無陰質"},{"pid":"b4120c626a2ce117104f9017cb53831fe29ced60","tid":638212,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"XX了，X的蟈"},{"pid":"569b04406af3b7640a604266b7ee93e7be4f2552","tid":638212,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/215852_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F215852_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=45827860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f174edd7172151ae8200922fd5b973febdbf425d","tid":638212,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，4月23日係世界閱讀日，中國人學好中文日，莎士比亞生日"},{"pid":"542e9c67a3294ce7091e3381636bd56a48464ddb","tid":638212,"uid":19218,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"上一則<br />\n急流中練習　桂林龍舟翻側17死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186aaf35135f42aba1a942412cbb24b3f3d46688","tid":638212,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542e9c67a3294ce7091e3381636bd56a48464ddb","tid":638212,"uid":19218,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"上一則<br />\n急流中練習　桂林龍舟翻側17死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo